{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":766,"text":"I would like to start"},{"time":2543,"text":"with the story of Mary,"},{"time":4504,"text":"a woman from an African village."},{"time":7495,"text":"Her first memories"},{"time":9088,"text":"are of her family fleeing violent riots"},{"time":11940,"text":"orchestrated by \nthe ruling political party."},{"time":15797,"text":"Her brother was murdered\nby the state-sponsored militia,"},{"time":19794,"text":"and she was raped more than once"},{"time":21371,"text":"just because she belonged\nto the wrong party."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26610,"text":"One morning, a month before the election,"},{"time":29743,"text":"Mary's village was called \nto another intimidation meeting."},{"time":33464,"text":"In this meeting, there is a man\nstanding in front of them,"},{"time":36243,"text":"telling them, \"We know who you are,"},{"time":38701,"text":"we know who you will vote for,"},{"time":41352,"text":"and if you're not going\nto drop the right paper,"},{"time":43762,"text":"we're going to take revenge.\""},{"time":47100,"text":"But for Mary, this meeting is different."},{"time":50059,"text":"She feels different."},{"time":51793,"text":"This time, she's waiting for this meeting,"},{"time":54430,"text":"because this time, she's carrying\na small hidden camera in her dress,"},{"time":58599,"text":"a camera that nobody else can see."},{"time":61655,"text":"Nobody is allowed to film\nin these meetings."},{"time":63722,"text":"You risk your life if you do."},{"time":65781,"text":"Mary knows that, but she also knows\nthat the only way to stop them"},{"time":70179,"text":"and to protect herself and her community"},{"time":73751,"text":"is to expose their intimidation,"},{"time":76066,"text":"to make sure they understand\nsomebody is following them,"},{"time":80048,"text":"to break the impunity they feel."},{"time":83738,"text":"Mary and her friends were filming\nfor months, undercover,"},{"time":87724,"text":"the intimidation of\nthe ruling political party."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91491,"text":"(Video) [\"Filmed with hidden cameras\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":93996,"text":"Man: We are now going to speak\nabout the upcoming elections."},{"time":98317,"text":"Nothing can stop us \nfrom doing what we want."},{"time":101747,"text":"If we hear you are with [The Opposition]"},{"time":105158,"text":"we will not forgive you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107694,"text":"[\"Militia intimidation rally\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":112635,"text":"[The Party] can torture you at any time."},{"time":115258,"text":"The youth can beat you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118698,"text":"[\"Disruption of political meeting\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":127588,"text":"For those who lie, saying they \nare back with [The Party],"},{"time":131765,"text":"your time is running out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134138,"text":"[\"Party youth militia\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":137279,"text":"Some have died because they rebelled."},{"time":139407,"text":"Some have lost their homes."},{"time":142426,"text":"If you don't work together \nwith [The Party],"},{"time":146190,"text":"you will lead a very bad life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158447,"text":"Oren Yakobovich: These images\nwere broadcast all over the world,"},{"time":161586,"text":"but more importantly,"},{"time":163183,"text":"they have been broadcast\nback to the community."},{"time":166336,"text":"The perpetrators saw them too."},{"time":169220,"text":"They understood somebody\nis following them."},{"time":171461,"text":"They got scared. Impunity was broken."},{"time":175070,"text":"Mary and her friends forced\nthe ruling political party"},{"time":178156,"text":"not to use violence during the election,"},{"time":180406,"text":"and saved hundreds of lives."},{"time":183895,"text":"Mary is just one of hundreds of people"},{"time":186402,"text":"that my organization had helped \nto document human rights violations"},{"time":189962,"text":"using cameras."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192862,"text":"My background should have\nled me to a different direction."},{"time":196223,"text":"I was born in Israel\nto a right-wing family,"},{"time":199472,"text":"and as long as I remember myself,"},{"time":201378,"text":"I wanted to join the Israeli army\nto serve my country"},{"time":204473,"text":"and prove what I believed \nwas our right for the whole land."},{"time":208924,"text":"I joined the Israeli army \njust after the first intifada,"},{"time":214204,"text":"the first Palestinian uprising,"},{"time":216584,"text":"and I served in one of the hard-minded,"},{"time":218492,"text":"toughest, aggressive infantry units,"},{"time":222012,"text":"and I got the biggest gun in my platoon."},{"time":226971,"text":"Quite fast, I became an officer"},{"time":229431,"text":"and got soldiers under my command,"},{"time":232422,"text":"and as time passed, I started\nserving in the West Bank,"},{"time":235347,"text":"and I saw these images."},{"time":245811,"text":"I didn't like what I saw."},{"time":248077,"text":"It took me a while,"},{"time":249496,"text":"but eventually I refused\nto serve in the West Bank"},{"time":252738,"text":"and had to spend time in jail."},{"time":255594,"text":"It was a bit —"},{"time":256754,"text":"(Applause) —"},{"time":259730,"text":"It was not that bad, I have to say."},{"time":261422,"text":"It was a bit like being in a hotel,\nbut with very shitty food."},{"time":264505,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":266170,"text":"In jail, I kept thinking \nthat I need people to know."},{"time":270042,"text":"I need people to understand"},{"time":271708,"text":"what the reality\nin the West Bank looks like."},{"time":274564,"text":"I need them to hear what I heard,"},{"time":277002,"text":"I need them to see what I saw,"},{"time":278906,"text":"but I also understood, we need \nthe Palestinians themselves,"},{"time":282244,"text":"the people that are suffering,"},{"time":283733,"text":"to be able to tell their own stories,"},{"time":285965,"text":"not journalists or filmmakers\nthat are coming outside of the situation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292071,"text":"I joined a human rights organization,"},{"time":294649,"text":"an Israeli human rights \norganization called B'Tselem."},{"time":297789,"text":"Together, we analyzed the West Bank"},{"time":299864,"text":"and picked 100 families that\nare living in the most risky places:"},{"time":303789,"text":"close to checkpoints, near army bases,"},{"time":307604,"text":"side by side with settlers."},{"time":310059,"text":"We gave them cameras and training."},{"time":313901,"text":"Quite fast, we started getting\nvery disturbing images"},{"time":318231,"text":"about how the settlers \nand the soldiers are abusing them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323213,"text":"I would like to share with you\ntwo clips from this project."},{"time":326333,"text":"Both of them were broadcast in Israel,\nand it created a massive debate."},{"time":330478,"text":"And I have to warn you,"},{"time":331770,"text":"some of you might \nfind them quite explicit."},{"time":335030,"text":"The masked men you \nwill see in the first clips"},{"time":337454,"text":"are Jewish settlers."},{"time":339184,"text":"Minutes before the camera was turned on,"},{"time":341670,"text":"they approached a Palestinian family"},{"time":343548,"text":"that was working their land"},{"time":345360,"text":"and told them that they\nhave to leave the land,"},{"time":347567,"text":"because this land belongs\nto the Jewish settlers."},{"time":350119,"text":"The Palestinians refused."},{"time":352046,"text":"Let's see what happened."},{"time":355109,"text":"The masked men that are approaching\nare Jewish settlers."},{"time":358925,"text":"They are approaching\nthe Palestinian family."},{"time":381087,"text":"This is a demonstration in the West Bank."},{"time":383461,"text":"The guy in green is Palestinian."},{"time":385063,"text":"He will be arrested in a second."},{"time":387873,"text":"Here you see him\nblindfolded and handcuffed."},{"time":390706,"text":"In a few seconds, he regrets \nhe came to this demonstration."},{"time":397824,"text":"He's been shot in the foot\nwith a rubber bullet."},{"time":403256,"text":"He is okay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408242,"text":"Not all the settlers and the soldiers\nare acting this way."},{"time":412813,"text":"We're talking about a tiny minority,\nbut they have to be brought to justice."},{"time":417058,"text":"These clips, and others like them,"},{"time":419311,"text":"forced the army and the police\nto start investigations."},{"time":422709,"text":"They've been shown in Israel, of course,"},{"time":424963,"text":"and the Israeli public\nwas exposed to them also."},{"time":428039,"text":"This project redefined\nthe struggle for human rights"},{"time":431107,"text":"in the occupied territories,"},{"time":432708,"text":"and we managed to reduce the number \nof violent attacks in the West Bank."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440517,"text":"The success of this project\ngot me thinking"},{"time":442716,"text":"how I can take the same methodology\nto other places in the world."},{"time":446306,"text":"Now, we tend to believe that today,"},{"time":448016,"text":"with all of the technology,"},{"time":449722,"text":"the smartphones and the Internet,"},{"time":451352,"text":"we are able to see and understand\nmost of what's happening in the world,"},{"time":454748,"text":"and people are able to tell their story —"},{"time":456897,"text":"but it's only partly true."},{"time":458796,"text":"Still today, with all\nthe technology we have,"},{"time":461794,"text":"less than half of the world's population"},{"time":464202,"text":"has access to the Internet,"},{"time":466478,"text":"and more than three billion people —"},{"time":469025,"text":"I'm repeating the number —"},{"time":470589,"text":"three billion people are consuming news\nthat is censored by those in power."},{"time":478590,"text":"More or less around the same time,"},{"time":480419,"text":"I'm approached by a great guy\nnamed Uri Fruchtmann."},{"time":483537,"text":"He's a filmmaker and an activist."},{"time":485893,"text":"We understood we were\nthinking along the same lines,"},{"time":488469,"text":"and we decided to establish Videre,\nour organization, together."},{"time":494658,"text":"While building the organization in London,"},{"time":497522,"text":"we've been traveling undercover to places"},{"time":499594,"text":"where a community \nwas suffering from abuses,"},{"time":501781,"text":"where mass atrocities were happening,"},{"time":504449,"text":"and there was a lack of reporting."},{"time":507326,"text":"We tried to understand how we can help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":511121,"text":"There were four things that I learned."},{"time":513790,"text":"The first thing is that we have to engage"},{"time":516250,"text":"with communities that are\nliving in rural areas,"},{"time":519409,"text":"where violations are happening\nfar from the public eye."},{"time":522814,"text":"We need to partner with them,"},{"time":524645,"text":"and we need to understand which images\nare not making it out there"},{"time":528566,"text":"and help them to document them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531824,"text":"The second thing I learned"},{"time":533642,"text":"is that we have to enable them \nto film in a safe way."},{"time":537424,"text":"Security has to be the priority."},{"time":541803,"text":"Where I used to work before,\nin the West Bank,"},{"time":544006,"text":"one can take a camera out,"},{"time":545646,"text":"most likely not going to get shot,"},{"time":548339,"text":"but in places we wanted to work,"},{"time":549884,"text":"just try to pull a phone out,\nand you're dead — literally dead."},{"time":555094,"text":"This is why we decided"},{"time":556624,"text":"to take the operation undercover"},{"time":558568,"text":"when necessary,"},{"time":559995,"text":"and use mostly hidden cameras."},{"time":562026,"text":"Unfortunately, I can't show you\nthe hidden cameras we're using today —"},{"time":565403,"text":"for obvious reasons —"},{"time":566845,"text":"but these are cameras we used before."},{"time":569097,"text":"You can buy them off the shelf."},{"time":571187,"text":"Today, we're building \na custom-made hidden camera,"},{"time":574786,"text":"like the one that Mary was wearing"},{"time":576648,"text":"in her dress to film\nthe intimidation meeting"},{"time":578942,"text":"of the ruling political party."},{"time":580954,"text":"It's a camera that nobody can see,"},{"time":582796,"text":"that blends into the environment,"},{"time":585745,"text":"into the surroundings."},{"time":587824,"text":"Now, filming securities go beyond\nusing hidden cameras."},{"time":591272,"text":"Being secure starts way before\nthe activist is turning the camera on."},{"time":596162,"text":"To keep our partners safe,"},{"time":598214,"text":"we work to understand\nthe risk of every location"},{"time":600966,"text":"and of every shot before it's happened,"},{"time":603647,"text":"building a backup plan\nif something goes wrong,"},{"time":606549,"text":"and making sure \nwe have everything in place"},{"time":608941,"text":"before our operations start."}]},{"cues":[{"time":611892,"text":"The third thing I learned\nis the importance of verification."},{"time":615707,"text":"You can have an amazing shot of atrocity,"},{"time":618311,"text":"but if you can't verify it,\nit's worth nothing."},{"time":622079,"text":"Recently, like in the ongoing war \nin Syria or the war in Gaza,"},{"time":625562,"text":"we've seen images that are staged \nor brought from a different conflict."},{"time":630875,"text":"This misinformation destroyed\nthe credibility of the source,"},{"time":633828,"text":"and it's harmed the credibility of other\nreliable and trustworthy sources."},{"time":638608,"text":"We use a variety of ways to make sure\nwe can verify the information"},{"time":642611,"text":"and we can trust the material."},{"time":644559,"text":"It starts with vetting the partners,"},{"time":646432,"text":"understanding who they are,\nand working with them very intensively."},{"time":649645,"text":"How do you film a location?"},{"time":651780,"text":"You film road signs, you film watches,"},{"time":653614,"text":"you film newspapers."},{"time":654956,"text":"We are checking maps, looking at maps,"},{"time":659442,"text":"double-checking the information,"},{"time":661695,"text":"and looking also at \nthe metadata of the material."}]},{"cues":[{"time":666078,"text":"Now, the fourth and the most\nimportant thing I learned"},{"time":669197,"text":"is how you use images \nto create a positive change."},{"time":674450,"text":"To have an effect,"},{"time":676299,"text":"the key thing is how you use the material."}]},{"cues":[{"time":680886,"text":"Today, we're working\nwith hundreds of activists"},{"time":683404,"text":"filming undercover."},{"time":684953,"text":"We work with them both to understand \nthe situation on the ground"},{"time":688055,"text":"and which images \nare missing to describe it,"},{"time":691045,"text":"who are the ones that are \ninfluencing the situation,"},{"time":695979,"text":"and when to release the material\nto advance the struggle."},{"time":700036,"text":"Sometimes, it's about\nputting it in the media,"},{"time":702473,"text":"mostly local ones, to create awareness."},{"time":704399,"text":"Sometimes it's working\nwith decision makers,"},{"time":706835,"text":"to change laws."},{"time":708009,"text":"Sometimes, it's working with lawyers\nto use as evidence in court."},{"time":712535,"text":"But more than often,"},{"time":714053,"text":"the most effective way\nto create a social change"},{"time":718011,"text":"is to work within the community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":720342,"text":"I want to give you one example."},{"time":722575,"text":"Fatuma is part of a network of women\nthat are fighting abuses in Kenya."},{"time":728351,"text":"Women in her community\nhave been harassed constantly"},{"time":731282,"text":"on their way to school\nand on their way to work."},{"time":734157,"text":"They are trying to change \nthe behavior of the community from inside."},{"time":737854,"text":"In the next clip,"},{"time":740384,"text":"Fatuma is taking us with her\non her journey to work."},{"time":744649,"text":"Her voice is superimposed\non images that she filmed herself"},{"time":748557,"text":"using hidden cameras."}]},{"cues":[{"time":751095,"text":"(Video) Fatuma Chiusiku: \nMy name is Fatuma Chiusiku."},{"time":753572,"text":"I'm 32 years old, a mother,"},{"time":755824,"text":"And Ziwa La Ng'Ombe is my home."},{"time":759439,"text":"Each morning, I ride the mini-bus"},{"time":761652,"text":"Number 11."},{"time":764009,"text":"But instead of a peaceful journey to work,"},{"time":767062,"text":"each day begins with fear."},{"time":770491,"text":"Come with me now"},{"time":771991,"text":"and use my eyes"},{"time":773796,"text":"to feel what I feel."},{"time":779569,"text":"As I walk, I think to myself:"},{"time":781714,"text":"Will I be touched?"},{"time":783385,"text":"Grabbed?"},{"time":784650,"text":"Violated by this conductor again?"},{"time":788114,"text":"Even the men inside"},{"time":790207,"text":"the way they look at me"},{"time":792350,"text":"touch my body, rub against me,"},{"time":794666,"text":"grab me,"},{"time":796619,"text":"and now, as I sit in my seat"},{"time":798892,"text":"I only wish my mind was full\nof thoughts for my day,"},{"time":801734,"text":"my dreams, my children at school,"},{"time":803350,"text":"but instead I worry about\nthe moment when we will arrive"},{"time":807617,"text":"and I will be violated again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812785,"text":"OY: Today, there is a new front\nin the fight for human rights."},{"time":818150,"text":"I used to carry a big gun."},{"time":820695,"text":"Now, I am carrying this."},{"time":823868,"text":"This is a much more powerful\nand much, much more effective weapon."},{"time":830298,"text":"But we have to use its power wisely."},{"time":834429,"text":"By putting the right images\nin the right hands at the right time,"},{"time":839793,"text":"we can truly create an impact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842585,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":844819,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":853244,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":855848,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}